    '''Property that represents a numeric value.

    :Parameters:
        `defaultvalue`: int or float, defaults to 0
            Specifies the default value of the property.

    >>> wid = Widget()
    >>> wid.x = 42
    >>> print(wid.x)
    42
    >>> wid.x = "plop"
